          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "appendText",
          "source": "If this plugin adds value for you and you would like to help support continued development, please use the buttons below:",
          "target": "如果此插件对您有价值，并且您愿意支持其持续开发，请使用下方的按钮："
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Requires restart of Obsidian. If enabled, when the cursor is in a table, enter advances to the next row. Disabling this can help avoid conflicting with tag or CJK autocompletion. If disabling, bind \"Go to ...\" in the Obsidian Hotkeys settings.",
          "target": "需要重启 Obsidian。启用后，当光标在表格中时，按回车键将跳转到下一行。禁用此功能有助于避免与标签或 CJK 自动补全冲突。如需禁用，请在 Obsidian 快捷键设置中绑定“前往...”。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Requires restart of Obsidian. If enabled, when the cursor is in a table, tab/shift+tab navigate between cells. Disabling this can help avoid conflicting with tag or CJK autocompletion. If disabling, bind \"Go to ...\" in the Obsidian Hotkeys settings.",
          "target": "需要重启 Obsidian。启用后，当光标在表格中时，按 Tab/Shift+Tab 键可在单元格间导航。禁用此功能有助于避免与标签或 CJK 自动补全冲突。如需禁用，请在 Obsidian 快捷键设置中绑定“前往...”。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "If enabled, table cells will have spaces added to match the width of the longest cell in the column.",
          "target": "启用后，表格单元格将添加空格以匹配该列中最宽单元格的宽度。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "If enabled, a button which opens the table controls toolbar will be added to the Obsidian sidebar. The toolbar can also be opened with a Hotkey. Changes only take effect on reload.",
          "target": "启用后，一个用于打开表格控制工具栏的按钮将被添加到 Obsidian 侧边栏。该工具栏也可以通过快捷键打开。更改仅在重新加载后生效。"
        },
        {
